sections.heading: registered nurse anesthetist; license; renewal
sections.text: To renew a license to practice as a certified registered nurse anesthetist, the applicant shall have current certification by the Council on Certification of Nurse Anesthetists.SourceLaws 1981, LB 379, ยง 32;Laws 1993, LB 536, ยง 73;Laws 1995, LB 563, ยง 4
